Package com.github.upthewaterspout.fates.core.threading.event

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ExecutionEventListener
    Listener for receiving events from users instrumented bytecode.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AtomicClassLoadingDecorator
    A decorator for a ExecutionEventListener that allows disabling the ExecutionEventListener.beforeGetField(Object, String, String, String, int) and ExecutionEventListener.beforeSetField(Object, Object, String, String, String, int) while class loading is happening.
    AtomicMethodListener
    A decorator for a ExecutionEventListener that allows disabling execution events while inside a certain list of classes.
    DelegatingExecutionEventListener
    An ExecutionEventListener that delegates all calls to a nested ExecutionEventListener.
    IgnoreFinalFieldsListener  
    NonReentrantExecutionEventListener
    A decorator for ExecutionEventListener that prevents instrumentation of code that is itself running inside this ExecutionEventListener This listener delegates to a passed in listener.
    NoopExecutionEventListener
    An ExecutionEventListener that behaves as though the code has not been instrumented.
    ThreadLocalEventListener
    A decorator for a ExecutionEventListener that is only enabled for the current thread and any thread spawned by the current thread.
